#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:6
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_START_RADIKAL\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"你已抵达拉迪卡尔星区，来自各地的专家们都会来到这里，寻找高效的非法规格装备"
"。\n"
"\t\t叛军要弄到这里的坐标会有些困难，这给了你一些时间，为活着离开这里做好准备"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:9
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_START_RADIKAL\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"你已抵达拉迪卡尔星区。只要准备好做出牺牲，就能在这里找到威力巨大但充满危险的"
"装备。\n"
"\t\t叛军要弄到这里的坐标会有些困难，这给了你一些时间，为活着离开这里做好准备"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:27
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"START_RADIKAL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:34
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"信标处有一艘装备精良的飞船在看守，但暂时还没有敌意。远处，你看到一艘海盗船正"
"在跃迁离开。据你判断，他们满载着货物，而守卫刚刚放他们通过了，附近没有任何近"
"期战斗过的痕迹。\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t守卫正在呼叫你。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:38
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "回应呼叫。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:40
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“嘿，那边。是新来的还是常客？”守卫漫不经心地等着你的回答。这似乎是在问你对这"
"个星区的熟悉程度。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:42
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "新来的。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:44
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "“啊，难怪。你的飞船看起来真该好好升级一下了。你到底知不知道来这里要找什么？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:46
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "是。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:48
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“好吧，你想去哪儿？”守卫在通讯器上调出了一份简短的目的地列表，上面只有代号，"
"所有通常的详细信息都缺失了。你开始琢磨，自己刚到的这个地方到底有多见不得光。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:50
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "选择“巴姆”。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:52
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“经典之选，总是那么可靠。明智的选择。”守卫把坐标传给了你，然后在你还没来得及"
"回答之前就迅速切断了通讯。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_guards.xml.append:60
msgid ""
"data/events_special_guards.xml.append$//event[@name=\"GUARD_RADIKAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "检查仓库。"

